google.subtitle: Alexander, Hannibal, Caesar, and the Genius of Leadership
google.description: Analyzes the leadership and strategies of three forefront military leaders from the ancient world, offers insight into the purposes behind their conflicts, and shows what today's leaders can glean from their successes and failures.
google.title: Masters of Command
